    KubeRBACProxy -.->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token<br/>SubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI

    %% Auth to Dashboard
    KubeRBACProxy -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>localhost (plaintext)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>x-forwarded-access-token"| DashBackend

    %% Dashboard to cluster services
    DashBackend -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer token (user)"| K8sAPI
    DashBackend -->|"HTTPS/9092<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer token"| Thanos

